;W[qq]LB[ps:1][ns:2][ls:3][qq:4]C[Dia.2 Eye vs. no eye

{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;}
When Black descends with 1 it may seem like he's played a good move.  But, White can make an eye with 2, it's a maek.  At this moment White has increased his liberties.

Even if Black descends at 3 this is a case of \cf1\b one eye vs. no eye\cf0\b0  so Black is dead.

\lang1042\f1\fs18
])
(;AW[pp][qp][mq][nq][oq][mr][or][rr]AB[ko][mp][np][op][lq][pq][lr][pr]
