;B[ps]LB[ns:1][os:2][ps:3]C[Dia.3 Correct / Placement attack

{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
Black's placement attack at 1 is the maek in this position.  White can block with 3 but then Black will take away a liberty at 3 which means \cf1\b Black has won the capturing race!
\cf0\lang1042\b0\f1\fs18
\lang1033\f0\fs16 White has 2 liberties and Black has 3, which means Black wins.

\cf1\b Your opponent's vital point is your vital point!

